string-array.name: decision_point_message
string-array.item: Qhubeka nokwenza idivayisi yakho isethwe ngokugcwele. Noma, hamba manje uphinde uthole isikhumbuzi sokuqedelela ngemuva kwesikhathi.
Qhubeka ukuze usethe umsizi wakho we-Google, shintsha isithombe sakho sangemuva, nokuningi. Noma, hamba manje uphinde uqedele emuva kwesikhathi.
Qhubeka ukuze usethe umsizi wakho we-Google nokuningi. Noma, hamba manje uphinde usethe lokhu emuva kwesikhathi.
Qhubeka ukuze ukhulume nomsizi wakho we-Google, sebenzisa i-Google Pay, nokuningi. Noma, hamba manje uphinde lokhu emuva kwesikhathi.

string-array.name: decision_point_message_verbose
string-array.item: Usuqedile ngokuyisisekelo. Qhubeka ukuze wenze idivayisi yakho isethwe ngokugcwele. Noma, hamba manje uphinde uthole isikhumbuzi sokuqedelela ngemuva kwesikhathi.
Uqedile ngokuyisisekelo. Qhubeka nokusetha umsizi wakho we-Google, shintsha isithombe skaho sangemuva, nokuningi. Noma, shiya manje bese uqedele kamuva.
Uqedile ngokuyisisekelo. Qhubeka nokusetha umsizi wakho we-Google nokuningi. Noma, shiya manje bese usethe lokhu kamuva.
Uqedile ngokuyisisekelo. Qhubeka nokukhuluma nomsizi wakho we-Google, sebenzisa i-Google Pay, nokuningi. Noma, shiya manje bese usethe lokhu kamuva.
